      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TEST OF LOVE (5) made his Australian debut off an 11-month break at Sale having formerly plied his trade in Hong Kong, far too good on speed there to score by 1.75 lengths. Imagine she'll strip a fair bit fitter for that and take catching once more. HEDONIST (3) is going very well this time in, a dominant five-length winner at Warrnambool two back, just run down by a smart one at Caulfield last time. He lands in a good trailing spot here and will be very hard to hold out. SPANISH BLAZE (1) resumes. He didn't fire in his local debut but has had more time to acclimatise now and the Freedman/Brown combination has to be respected. WINSOME STAR (6) has claims off a narrow win here last time out.",
